The City of Key West, Plaintiff in Error, v. Emma E. Torano, Defendant in Error. A Writ of Error to a Judgment of the Circuit Court within and for the County of Monroe. Wm. H. Malone, for Plaintiff in Error; W. Eimt Harris, for Defendant in Error.

Writ of Error dismissed on motion of counsel for Defendant in Error.
